      "writtenOn": "2026-05-12T15:02:54Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "btw, I didn\u0027t write this before because it seemed like a relatively simple change.  Ideally we should be transitioning away from errors.yaml and using events.yaml.  Events have a very clear way to specify which argument and then a programmatic way for something like bmcweb to match on it.  We could start creating a Common.Events for this one so that we have something to start transitioning to.",
      "parentUuid": "6857fcce_e6352ade",
      "revId": "761946d22f42b06deeab58691f9375b14b1feb44",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
    },
